{{citation needed|September 19 (Lunisolar)}}

{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 19''' is the 19th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Kōnin|ja|弘仁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[810]] {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Daidō|ja|大同|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} から{{ill|Kōnin|ja|弘仁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}に{{ill|Era change|ja|改元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Shōtai|ja|昌泰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[899]] {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – 群盗横行のため、{{ill|Sagami Province|ja|相模国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の{{ill|Ashigara Saka|ja|足柄坂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}・{{ill|Ueno Province|ja|上野国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Usui Saka|ja|碓氷坂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に関を設置. * {{ill|Katei|ja|嘉禎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1235]] {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Earthquake|ja|地震|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 頻発のため、{{ill|Bunryaku|ja|文暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} から{{ill|Katei|ja|嘉禎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}に{{ill|Era change|ja|改元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Shōchū|ja|正中|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1324]] {{ill|October 7|ja|10月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shōchū Rebellion|ja|正中の変|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. {{ill|Rokuhara Tandai|ja|六波羅探題|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} dispatched troops and thwarted the forces of {{ill|Emperor Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}—led by {{ill|Toki Yorikane|ja|土岐頼兼|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Tajimi Kuninaga|ja|多治見国長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}—capturing {{ill|Hino Mototomo|ja|日野資朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hino Toshiki|ja|日野俊基|display=俊基|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1870]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Commoners|ja|平民|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} were permitted to adopt a {{ill|Family name|ja|苗字|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a practice made mandatory in the 5th year thereafter.
== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1842]] {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Nagaoka Mamoru|ja|長岡護美|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a diplomat, member of the {{ill|Kazoku|ja|華族|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and politician (died [[1906]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Ōan|ja|応安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 23rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1368]] {{ill|October 31|ja|10月31日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Uesugi Norifusa|ja|上杉憲顕|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Kantō Kanryō (関東管領) (born [[1306]]).
