endar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1235]] {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 1|qq=}}) – {{ill|Earthquake|ja|地震|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthquake|qq=}} 頻発のため、{{ill|Bunryaku|ja|文暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunryaku|qq=}} から{{ill|Katei|ja|嘉禎|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Katei|qq=}}に{{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * {{ill|Shōchū|ja|正中|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōchū|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1324]] {{ill|October 7|ja|10月7日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 7|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shōchū Rebellion|ja|正中の変|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōchū Rebellion|qq=}}. {{ill|Rokuhara Tandai|ja|六波羅探題|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuhara Tandai|qq=}} dispatched troops and thwarted the forces of {{ill|Emperor Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Godaigo|qq=}}—led by {{ill|Toki Yorikane|ja|土岐頼兼|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toki Yorikane|qq=}} and {{ill|Tajimi Kuninaga|ja|多治見国長|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tajimi Kuninaga|qq=}}—capturing {{ill|Hino Mototomo|ja|日野資朝|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hino Mototomo|qq=}} and {{ill|Hino Toshiki|ja|日野俊基|display=俊基|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hino Toshiki|qq=}}. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1870]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 13|qq=}}) – {{ill|Commoners|ja|平民|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Commoners|qq=}} were permitted to adopt a {{ill|Family name|ja|苗字|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Family name|qq=}}, a practice made mandatory in the 5th year thereafter.
