== Events == * [[:en:Kōnin (era)|Kōnin]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[810]] [[:en:October 20|October 20]]) – [[:en:Datong (disambiguation)|Daidō]] から[[:en:Kōnin (era)|Kōnin]]に{{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * [[:en:Shōtai|Shōtai]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[899]] [[:en:October 27|October 27]]) – 群盗横行のため、[[:en:Sagami Province|Sagami Province]] の{{ill|Ashigara Saka|ja|足柄坂|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashigara Saka|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 足柄峠}}・[[:en:Kōzuke Province|Ueno Province]] {{ill|Usui Saka|ja|碓氷坂|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Usui Saka|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} に関を設置. * [[:en:Katei|Katei]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1235|1235]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]]) – [[:en:Earthquake|Earthquake]] 頻発のため、[[:en:Bunryaku|Bunryaku]] から[[:en:Katei|Katei]]に{{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * [[:en:Culmination|Shōchū]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1324]] [[:en:October 7|October 7]]) – {{ill|Shōchū Rebellion|ja|正中の変|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōchū Rebellion|qq=}}. [[:en:Rokuhara Tandai|Rokuhara Tandai]] dispatched troops and thwarted the forces of [[:en:Emperor Go-Daigo|Emperor Godaigo]]—led by {{ill|Toki Yorikane|ja|土岐頼兼|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toki Yorikane|qq=}} and {{ill|Tajimi Kuninaga|ja|多治見国長|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tajimi Kuninaga|qq=}}—capturing {{ill|Hino Mototomo|ja|日野資朝|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hino Mototomo|qq=}} and {{ill|Hino Toshiki|ja|日野俊基|display=俊基|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hino Toshiki|qq=}}. * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1870]] [[:en:October 13|October 13]]) – [[:en:Commoner|Commoners]] were permitted to adopt a {{ill|Family name|ja|苗字|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Family name|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 名字}}, a practice made mandatory in the 5th year thereafter.
