{{Not to be confused with|September 19|qq=September 19}}[[Category:Days of the Japanese Lunisolar Calendar]]<!--why is this category always showing up as 347 members?--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月十九|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 19일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 19''' is the 19th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senbu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜}}.
== Events == * [[:en:Kōnin (era)|Kōnin]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:810|810]] [[:en:October 20|October 20]]) – [[:en:Datong (disambiguation)|Daidō]] から[[:en:Kōnin (era)|Kōnin]]に{{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * [[:en:Shōtai|Shōtai]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:899|899]] [[:en:October 27|October 27]]) – 群盗横行のため、[[:en:Sagami Province|Sagami Province]] の{{ill|Ashigara Saka|ja|足柄坂|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashigara Saka|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 足柄峠}}・[[:en:Kōzuke Province|Ueno Province]] {{ill|Usui Saka|ja|碓氷坂|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Usui Saka|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} に関を設置. * [[:en:Katei|Katei]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1235|1235]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]]) – [[:en:Earthquake|Earthquake]] 頻発のため、[[:en:Bunryaku|Bunryaku]] から[[:en:Katei|Katei]]に{{ill|Era change|ja|改元|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Era change|qq=}}. * [[:en:Culmination|Shōchū]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1324|1324]] [[:en:October 7|October 7]]) – {{ill|Shōchū Rebellion|ja|正中の変|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōchū Rebellion|qq=}}. [[:en:Rokuhara Tandai|Rokuhara Tandai]] dispatched troops and thwarted the forces of [[:en:Emperor Go-Daigo|Emperor Godaigo]]—led by {{ill|Toki Yorikane|ja|土岐頼兼|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toki Yorikane|qq=}} and {{ill|Tajimi Kuninaga|ja|多治見国長|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tajimi Kuninaga|qq=}}—capturing {{ill|Hino Mototomo|ja|日野資朝|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hino Mototomo|qq=}} and {{ill|Hino Toshiki|ja|日野俊基|display=俊基|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hino Toshiki|qq=}}. * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1870|1870]] [[:en:October 13|October 13]]) – [[:en:Commoner|Commoners]] were permitted to adopt a {{ill|Family name|ja|苗字|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Family name|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 名字}}, a practice made mandatory in the 5th year thereafter.
== Births == * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 13rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1842|1842]] [[:en:October 22|October 22]]) – {{ill|Nagaoka Mamoru|ja|長岡護美|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nagaoka Mamoru|qq=}}, a diplomat, member of the [[:en:Kazoku|Kazoku]], and politician (died [[:en:1906|1906]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Ōan|Ōan era]] 1st year/[[:en:Zhengping|Shōhei]] 23rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1368|1368]] [[:en:October 31|October 31]]) – {{ill|Uesugi Norifusa|ja|上杉憲顕|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Uesugi Norifusa|qq=}}, a Kantō Kanryō (関東管領) (born [[:en:1306|1306]]).
